{"tid":507231,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇一套動畫可以好似命運石之門咁好睇？","createTime":"2017-12-23T04:24:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T13:00:12.000Z","uid":6327,"like":9,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf428681c182efb587ebfe6dfc304efa007711d","tid":507231,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"重睇左好多次 <br />\n有時求其開一集黎睇 <br />\n明知個劇情係點都會好自然睇多集繼續睇落去<br />\n未試過見有一套好似命運石之門咁樣集集都咁好睇<br />\n由前期日常去到中期既壓抑去到最後既熱血<br />\n真係好撚有feel 好緊湊<br />\n23集既未來短訊果part我諗係冇一套動畫可以比得上<br />\n「欺騙世界 欺騙自己」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇親個結局有時真係會幾感動下"},{"pid":"3509cae86d6d708bb35d28608908128582eae73c","tid":507231,"uid":33539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T06:46:01.000Z","msg":"SCHOOLDAYS"},{"pid":"9dfe3a81081bdbcd5be4d0578cb67cbf9972e74b","tid":507231,"uid":1675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"十卜牙"},{"pid":"c367c78abe3f9d433b9c98340c55737a6d6758ee","tid":507231,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n神作"},{"pid":"032f5c05ae8c0ef03bfbf5b5a9cdfd660a6d4184","tid":507231,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T06:55:37.000Z","msg":"55......"},{"pid":"0b14123a9aa410f13c3f365804c96dd09ec98b08","tid":507231,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:02:18.000Z","msg":"馬爻口吾至刂。。。"},{"pid":"a89e5e65a95a03385b933f4c0ea1bf7b7a8d1be5","tid":507231,"uid":5590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:09:10.000Z","msg":"四疊半"},{"pid":"15a534d83b72872652d3ad321f372dd39b454052","tid":507231,"uid":25704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"re0"},{"pid":"ee425a5630e04c573aec3bb3b81a4a5f23be8f8d","tid":507231,"uid":1972,"like":